### LOGIN
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "samwel@example.com",
  "password": "mypassword"
}

### PRICING CALCULATION
POST http://localhost:3000/api/pricing/calculate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "basePrice": 1000,
  "distanceKm": 50,
  "weightKg": 10
}
